Richard,
         The setup is correct.  The belt goes in FRONT of the fan housing 
(between the housing and the engine) and connects to a pulley behind the 
fan hub.  It would be a decent system if it used a standard sized belt.

>This is an a/c setup I've never seen before. The evaporator is under the 
